
to install maven - sudo wget apache-maven-3.8.4-bin.tar.gz
now untar(unzip) a file -  tar -xvf apache-maven-3.9.6-bin.tar.gz


to print environment variables -->
    printenv --> to print all
    echo ${name} --> to print specific // e.g echo $java_home
    sudo vi /etc/profile ----> to open file and write envir variable  /e.g write maven_home=. . . (same as java )
    source /etc/profile ---> to load environment variables.
